ible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-spm-anchor-id&quot;:&quot;5176.28103460.0.i171.96a07551lwLDSb&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px; line-height: 1.6em; text-align: left;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://su.bcebos.com/klx-sdk-release-public/xpytorch/dev_kl3/torch_xray/latest/torch_xray-999.9.9-cp310-cp310-linux_x86_64.whl\" target=\"_blank\">https://su.bcebos.com/klx-sdk-release-public/xpytorch/dev_kl3/torch_xray/latest/torch_xray-999.9.9-cp310-cp310-linux_x86_64.whl</a></span></span></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr style=\"display: table-row;vertical-align: inherit;visibility: visible;\">\n      <td data-colwidth=\"179\" style=\"display: table-cell;vertical-align: inherit;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 8px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(120, 172, 254);visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.51px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-spm-anchor-id&quot;:&quot;5176.28103460.0.i171.96a07551lwLDSb&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">xpu_profiler</span></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td data-colwidth=\"392\" style=\"display: table-cell;vertical-align: inherit;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;margin-top: 8px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://klx-sdk-release-public.su.bcebos.com/v1/xre/xprofiler/release/xprofiler-Linux_x86_64-2.0.2.0.tar.gz\" target=\"_blank\">https://klx-sdk-release-public.su.bcebos.com/v1/xre/xprofiler/release/xprofiler-Linux_x86_64-2.0.2.0.tar.gz</a></span></span></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <hr style=\"display: block;unicode-bidi: embed;border: 1px inset;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);visibility: visible;\">\n   <p data-spm-anchor-id=\"5176.28103460.0.i171.96a07551lwLDSb\" style=\"margin:24px 8px;unicode-bidi:embed;visibility:visible;display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(120, 172, 254);visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.51px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">1. 基于 vLLM 社区标准</span></span><span data-morpho-text=\"%E5%A4%A7%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88LLM%EF%BC%89%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E7%BA%AF%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9B%E8%80%8C%E5%A4%9A%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88VLM%EF%BC%89%E5%88%99%E9%9C%80%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E4%B9%83%E8%87%B3%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%BE%E8%91%97%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E3%80%82\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(120, 172, 254);visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.51px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">推出 Plugin，让新模型部署从数周缩短至数天</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">过去，每当 vLLM 社区发布对新模型的支持，若希望在国产芯片上同步部署，开发者往往需要对 vLLM 源码进行侵入式二次开发。这一过程不仅耗时长达三到四周，还容易因代码冲突导致后续社区版本升级困难，甚至影响已有业务的稳定性。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为破解这一难题，vLLM 社区推出了 RFC&nbsp;</span><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mj9p7na3-n6iapi\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">#11162</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;硬件插件标准。百度百舸联合昆仑芯基于该标准开发了 vLLM-Kunlun Plugin，实现 vLLM 社区版与昆仑芯 XPU 后端的完全解耦。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户只需安装标准 vLLM，再同步安装 vLLM-Kunlun 插件，即可在昆仑芯 XPU 上第一时间部署任意主流大模型，无需修改 vLLM 核心代码，真正实现即插即用。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.12em 0;unicode-bidi:embed;display:block;font-size:15px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100005836\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" width=\"100%\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"241\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=33f44778&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5p8giadRibbOicvFeZup0NiaDnv5WIRoEu7Fo8bWMmI0797AqgiciaswYjC9OVrUuwywwPG7HJzDdRXtft5SmG8rQjDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">2. Plugin 重构推理调度流程，实现社区版本升级零侵入</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在传统 vLLM 架构中，推理请求由 Engine 接收并调度，Worker 在 GPU 上创建 ModelRunner，进而实例化如&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Qwen3MoeForCausalLM</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;等模型类，并依赖 FlashAttention 等算子完成计算。整个流程深度绑定 CUDA 生态，一旦目标硬件平台变更，几乎每个环节都需要定制修改。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">启用 vLLM-Kunlun Plugin 后，以昆仑芯 P800 为例，推理流程发生了关键转变：在 Engine 初始化阶段，系统会依据 RFC&nbsp;</span><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mj9p7na4-jwkahv\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">#11162</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;自动发现并注册 Kunlun Plugin。随后，Worker 创建专为昆仑芯 P800 优化的 ModelRunner，并加载 Plugin 提供的定制化模型类&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Model Class（如&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Qwen3MoeForCausalLM</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">_Kunlun），该模型类进一步调用高性能昆仑芯算子，执行底层 Kernel 计算。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一架构革新带来了显著业务价值：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"display: block;unicode-bidi: embed;margin: 1.12em 0px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"display: list-item;\">\n     <p style=\"unicode-bidi:embed;display:block;font-size:15px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当 vLLM 社区发布新引擎版本</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，例如从 V0 升级至 V1，开发者只需在 Plugin 层面对齐新的 ModelRunner 接口规范；</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: list-item;\">\n     <p style=\"unicode-bidi:embed;display:block;font-size:15px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当社区推出新模型架构，如 DeepSeek-V3.2，则仅需在 Plugin 内部更新模型组网逻辑，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">复用已有高性能算子和调度框</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">架。同时，针对新增算子进行增量开发。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">两种场景下，均无需侵入 vLLM 核心，大幅降低适配成本。新模型或新版本的支持周期从数周缩短至数天，同时确保与社区主干长期兼容，真正实现一次开发，持续演进。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">3. 深度定制融合算子，让 P800 推理吞吐和时延全面对齐主流 AI 加速卡</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对 P800 芯片的计算特性，百度百舸联合昆仑芯，专门为各类模型设计了高性能融合算子，例如 Split_Norm_Rope 和 Fused MoE，有效缓解 Attention 与 MoE 模块的计算瓶颈。这些算子已集成至高性能昆仑芯算子库（比如 xtorch_ops）中，可被&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">vLLM-Kunlun Plugin&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">无缝调用。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 DeepSeek、Qwen、Llama、GLM 等主流模型的实测中，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这些高性能算子使得 P800 的推理服务吞吐与时延表现全面对标主流 AI 加速卡，真正释放国产芯片的理论算力潜力。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">4. 开放百度内部工具 torch_xray 与 xpu_profiler，让精度验证与性能调优开箱即用</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为确保模型在 P800 上稳定高效运行，本项目同步开放 2 套关键工具：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"display: block;unicode-bidi: embed;margin: 1.12em 0px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"display: list-item;\">\n     <p style=\"unicode-bidi:embed;display:block;font-size:15px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">torch_xray：用于算子精度调试，可自动比对 GPU 与 P800 的逐层输出，快速定位数值偏差；</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"display: list-item;\">\n     <p style=\"unicode-bidi:embed;display:block;font-size:15px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">xpu_profiler：提供类 nsys 的性能剖析能力，生成清晰的算子调用时序图，帮助开发者精准识别性能瓶颈与计算气泡。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这两套工具链已在百度大规模业务中反复验证，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">显著提升了大模型向国产芯片迁移与调优的效率，有效保障精度与性能的一致性，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">具备低门槛、高可靠、快迭代的特点，助力开发者高效推进业务落地。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">5. 覆盖 20+ 主流及多模态模型，私有模型也能快速适配上线</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，vLLM 推理引擎在 P800 已支持超过 20+ 主流及多模态模型系列，涵盖 Qwen 系列、DeepSeek 系列、Llama 系列、GLM、InternVL 多模态模型、GPT OSS 等。无论您使用的是社区开源模型还是自研私有模型，均可通过 vLLM-Kunlun Plugin 快速完成部署与优化，大幅降低迁移成本。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">6. 建立开放协作机制，让社区贡献直通主干生态</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">vLLM-Kunlun Plugin 已在 GitHub 全面开源，不仅包含高性能推理实现，还同步开放了百度内部验证过的生产级适配工具链与完整文档。开发者可实时跟踪功能演进与模型支持进度，并基于标准化流程独立完成私有模型的适配。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们坚信，强大的硬件生态离不开活跃的开发者社区。vLLM-Kunlun Plugin 项目坚持透明规划，我们将通过 GitHub Issue 和官方 Slack 社区（<a href=\"https://vllm-kunlun.slack.com/）提供技术答疑、经验分享与版本更新同步。\" target=\"_blank\">https://vllm-kunlun.slack.com/）提供技术答疑、经验分享与版本更新同步。</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们欢迎开发者深度参与上游贡献，让特定需求直接融入主干生态，共同推动国产 AI 基础设施的繁荣发展。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "百度百舸与昆仑芯联合开源 vLLM-Kunlun Plugin，使国产芯片在部署开源大模型时能快速适配新模型、实现高性能推理，并提供配套工具链支持。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "百度百舸与昆仑芯联合开源 vLLM-Kunlun Plugin，使国产芯片在部署开源大模型时能快速适配新模型、实现高性能推理，并提供配套工具链支持。",
  "summary": "为解决国产芯片部署开源大模型的效率与性能瓶颈，百度百舸与昆仑芯合作推出了 vLLM-Kunlun Plugin。该插件基于 vLLM 社区的硬件插件标准，实现了 vLLM 核心与昆仑芯 XPU 后端的完全解耦，使用户能够即插即用，将新模型部署周期从数周缩短至数天。文章详细阐述了 Plugin 如何重构推理调度流程，创新性地解决了传统架构中深度绑定 CUDA 生态的问题，并介绍了为昆仑芯 P800 定制的高性能融合算子，使其在主流大模型推理中性能全面对标主流 AI 加速卡。此外，文中还提到了同步开源的精度验证工具 torch_xray 和性能剖析工具 xpu_profiler，以助力开发者高效进行模型迁移、调试与优化。目前该插件已支持超过 20 种主流及多模态模型，并建立了开放协作机制，鼓励社区贡献。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "vLLM-Kunlun Plugin 实现社区版 vLLM 与昆仑芯 XPU 的解耦，大幅缩短模型适配周期。",
      "explanation": "通过遵循 vLLM 社区的硬件插件标准，该 Plugin 使得开发者无需侵入式修改 vLLM 源码，就能在昆仑芯 XPU 上快速部署新模型，将适配时间从数周降至数天，提升开发效率和系统稳定性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Plugin 重构推理调度流程，确保与 vLLM 社区主干兼容，降低适配成本。",
      "explanation": "通过在 Engine 初始化阶段注册 Plugin，并由 Plugin 提供定制化的 ModelRunner 和模型类，实现了昆仑芯 P800 的高性能计算，同时保证了 vLLM 社区版本升级和新模型架构变更时的零侵入性适配。"
    },
    {
      "point": "深度定制融合算子，使昆仑芯 P800 推理性能全面对标主流 AI 加速卡。",
      "explanation": "针对 P800 芯片特性设计了 Split_Norm_Rope 和 Fused MoE 等高性能融合算子，有效解决了 Attention 与 MoE 模块的计算瓶颈，显著提升了在主流大模型上的推理吞吐和降低了时延。"
    },
    {
